KARACHI, March 29: Former President @AAliZardari received the first dose of COVID-19 vaccine here today.
He advised everyone above the age of 50 years and those with serious underlying health issues, to get the vaccine free of cost at Sindh government’s vaccination centres. https://t.co/ImrPzVkGjU
